# Update Method

The first argument should be the id of what you want to update, followed by the data to be updated with.

``` javascript

const updatedRole = await role.update(id, { 
 name: "ASE"
})

const updatedPermission = await permission.update(id, { 
 resource: "task",
 action: "read"
})

const updatedPolicy = await role.updateWithAllowOrDeny(id, { 
 name: "task-author",
 kind: "ALLOW"
})

```